URL: https://forge.ird.fr/intertryp/shinypopgen
Description: ShinyPopGen is an interactive Shiny application for exploratory
    and descriptive population genetics analyses from individual-based multilocus
    datasets. It supports data import and formatting, marker inspection, estimation
    of standard diversity and differentiation statistics (Weir & Cockerham 1984),
    linkage disequilibrium analyses, and null allele screening.
